Many people think "ChatGPT is stored in one computer." Actually, ChatGPT runs on massive AI data centers containing thousands of powerful servers and GPUs.

🌍 What is a Data Center?

A data center is a large building (or a group of buildings) filled with:

🖥️ Thousands of servers
🎮 Thousands of AI GPUs (such as NVIDIA GPUs)
💾 Large storage systems
🌐 High-speed networking
❄️ Cooling systems
⚡ Massive power infrastructure

These servers work together to train and run AI models like ChatGPT.

