Does India Have a ChatGPT Data Center?

OpenAI has announced plans to expand its global infrastructure, 
but as of now there has been no public announcement of a dedicated OpenAI-operated ChatGPT data center in India.
Users in India access ChatGPT through OpenAI's global cloud infrastructure.


